1
00:00:01,440 --> 00:00:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let my feelings reach her!</font>

2
00:00:06,950 --> 00:00:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">.44 Magnum!</font>

3
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-She's strong.</font>

4
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think we may have ended up 
helping our enemy.</font>

5
00:00:26,550 --> 00:00:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I love you...</font>

6
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

7
00:00:31,510 --> 00:00:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you! I love you!</font>

8
00:00:34,740 --> 00:00:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love...</font>

9
00:00:49,030 --> 00:00:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way I feel about you...</font>

10
00:00:54,310 --> 00:00:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is totally love!</font>

11
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

12
00:01:06,190 --> 00:01:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll try to keep this short, then...</font>

13
00:01:11,010 --> 00:01:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ba-bump...</i></font>

14
00:01:14,970 --> 00:01:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ba-bump...</i></font>

15
00:01:22,890 --> 00:01:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're too damn old! 
It's never gonna happen! Ever!</font>

16
00:01:35,410 --> 00:01:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll leave it at that for today!</font>

17
00:01:38,730 --> 00:01:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Next time you die!</font>

18
00:01:41,370 --> 00:01:44,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

19
00:01:44,970 --> 00:01:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

20
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

21
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill...</font>

22
00:02:05,810 --> 00:02:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill me! Just freakin' kill me!</font>

23
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you try to kill us,
 you damn Shocker combatant?!</font>

24
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're on!</font>

25
00:02:18,130 --> 00:02:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will be a battle royale!</font>

26
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

27
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rider...</font>

28
00:02:31,090 --> 00:02:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Transform! V3!</font>

29
00:02:38,650 --> 00:02:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Transformation!</font>

30
00:02:41,410 --> 00:02:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kamen Rider!</font>

31
00:02:44,390 --> 00:02:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

32
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">.44...</font>

33
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">V3...</font>

34
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rider...</font>

35
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magnum!</font>

36
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Electric Heat Chop!</font>

37
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Punch!</font>

38
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?</font>

39
00:03:08,170 --> 00:03:10,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichiyo! There's trouble!</font>

40
00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shocker is on the move!</font>

41
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:19,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

42
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:20,720
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}SHOCKER IS ON THE MOVE</b></font>

43
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, let's move out!</font>

44
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:25,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

45
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all beat to hell.</font>

46
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they gonna be able to 
fight Shocker like this?</font>

47
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:23,470
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}FUTABA'S PUB</b></font>

48
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what did you mean about 
Shocker being on the move?</font>

49
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just like I told you 
before, Tojima-san.</font>

50
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Bat Man, under 
the alias of Koda Morio,</font>

51
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:38,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">seems to have a lot of influence 
in show business.</font>

52
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's been hosting a variety of events,</font>

53
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and every time, he converts 
the audience into combatants.</font>

54
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, he tells all the guys who attend...</font>

55
00:05:50,370 --> 00:05:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"If you join Shocker right now, 
you'll all get girlfriends!"</font>

56
00:05:54,460 --> 00:05:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"And they'll all be idols!"</font>

57
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you believe it?</font>

58
00:05:59,090 --> 00:06:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bastard plays dirty.</font>

59
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idols, though?</font>

60
00:06:06,930 --> 00:06:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd probably be on the fence 
if I didn't have Raiko!</font>

61
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're already part of Shocker.</font>

62
00:06:13,210 --> 00:06:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on.</font>

63
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the important part.</font>

64
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the end of the week, there's 
going to be a Combat Girls solo concert</font>

65
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">held at the Tokyo Central Dome.</font>

66
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With a capacity of 55,000 people...</font>

67
00:06:27,330 --> 00:06:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has the potential to be their 
biggest recruitment drive so far.</font>

68
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:37,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what should we do?!</font>

69
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at this.</font>

70
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

71
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:50,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plans for the concert that
 Yukarisu and I dug up.</font>

72
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:52,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With it, we'll have all the intel we need</font>

73
00:06:52,410 --> 00:06:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to infiltrate the venue 
and thwart his plan.</font>

74
00:06:58,300 --> 00:06:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done, Mitsuba!</font>

75
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

76
00:07:01,030 --> 00:07:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Praise me, too!</font>

77
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuriko-san?!</font>

78
00:07:07,910 --> 00:07:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tackle!</font>

79
00:07:09,130 --> 00:07:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?!</font>

80
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gave her a call.</font>

81
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:16,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She showed up at school, 
so I figured she was back on her feet.</font>

82
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are your injuries?</font>

83
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you healed already?</font>

84
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you tell?</font>

85
00:07:25,010 --> 00:07:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weren't you one of the Shocker robbers?</font>

86
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

87
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A lot's happened since then.</font>

88
00:07:33,910 --> 00:07:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here to avenge my guys.</font>

89
00:07:36,790 --> 00:07:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be joining you 
when you take down Shocker!</font>

90
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:47,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, Yuriko-san, 
I'm relieved that you're doing better!</font>

91
00:07:47,010 --> 00:07:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

92
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, I have to ask...</font>

93
00:07:53,020 --> 00:07:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where do you get off trying to put 
forward a plan without Tackle?!</font>

94
00:07:58,460 --> 00:07:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we didn't...</font>

95
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kamen Rider Stronger</i>, episode 35!</font>

96
00:08:05,310 --> 00:08:07,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who came to Stronger's rescue</font>

97
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as he was being brutalized 
by the Delza Army's Snake Woman?</font>

98
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Ichiyo-kun?!</font>

99
00:08:14,970 --> 00:08:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was V3.</font>

100
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the follow-up, episode 36, 
Kamen Riders X and Amazon showed up.</font>

101
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And in episode 37, after that...</font>

102
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:28,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Riderman came to their rescue!</font>

103
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then in episode 38!</font>

104
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kamen Riders 1 and 2 made their 
long-awaited return to Japan!</font>

105
00:08:36,540 --> 00:08:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The assemblage of seven Riders 
all worked together,</font>

106
00:08:41,850 --> 00:08:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in order to confront 
the giant Rock Great Leader!</font>

107
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

108
00:08:48,950 --> 00:08:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were roused when Stronger said 
that "all Kamen Riders are brothers,"</font>

109
00:08:54,290 --> 00:08:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then joined hands, 
gathering their energy,</font>

110
00:08:58,020 --> 00:09:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then got the Rock Great Leader 
on the ropes!</font>

111
00:09:02,650 --> 00:09:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And in the end...</font>

112
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The seven Kamen Riders brought 
an end to their long, long battle.</font>

113
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What have you guys been blabbing about?</font>

114
00:09:18,990 --> 00:09:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tackle wasn't there, though.</font>

115
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:26,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ultra Cyclone!</i></font>

116
00:09:34,330 --> 00:09:37,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I won't let this end the same way.</font>

117
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Tackle II!</font>

118
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll be joining you.</font>

119
00:09:44,830 --> 00:09:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

120
00:09:49,250 --> 00:09:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won the tournament, after all!</font>

121
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd be in real trouble 
without you, Sensei!</font>

122
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When confronted with a powerful enemy...</font>

123
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do Kamen Riders do?</font>

124
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Work together!</font>

125
00:10:03,290 --> 00:10:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're taking Shocker down!</font>

126
00:10:08,250 --> 00:10:09,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's her!</font>

127
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey—</font>

128
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's on the house.</font>

129
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:30,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sis...</font>

130
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Free stuff from you? 
What in the world has gotten—</font>

131
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you.</font>

132
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:42,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idiot.</font>

133
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are—</font>

134
00:10:46,820 --> 00:10:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

135
00:10:49,230 --> 00:10:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm counting on you.</font>

136
00:10:52,330 --> 00:10:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

137
00:10:56,990 --> 00:11:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, everyone, let's get to 
work on the plan...</font>

138
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, let's have a toast first! We gotta!</font>

139
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To celebrate Sensei feeling better, 
and all of us getting together!</font>

140
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good point.</font>

141
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:13,650
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}FUTABA'S PUB</b></font>

142
00:11:10,070 --> 00:11:12,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

143
00:11:42,410 --> 00:11:43,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More!</font>

144
00:11:43,690 --> 00:11:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

145
00:11:51,410 --> 00:11:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell is he doing? 
And at such a critical time...</font>

146
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:03,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you supposed to be?</font>

147
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me? I'm Hakkyoku Hachiro.</font>

148
00:12:07,370 --> 00:12:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't ask your damn name!</font>

149
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what are the two of you up to?</font>

150
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's been training me.</font>

151
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Training you?!</font>

152
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you see that?</font>

153
00:12:27,070 --> 00:12:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See what?! 
And why the hell did you fall over?!</font>

154
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's just a human!</font>

155
00:12:33,330 --> 00:12:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This man, while battling against himself, 
mastered the style of Bajiquan.</font>

156
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:43,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He then fought as 
an underground street fighter,</font>

157
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">until he ran out of opponents,</font>

158
00:12:46,590 --> 00:12:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now he's battling with ramen in
 an effort to satisfy the woman he loves.</font>

159
00:12:52,370 --> 00:12:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you trying to—</font>

160
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans are fascinating, Bat.</font>

161
00:12:58,540 --> 00:13:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I've been fighting him, 
I've come to understand something.</font>

162
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans seem to have 
something like a core.</font>

163
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's that supposed to mean?</font>

164
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:14,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rider Punch!</font>

165
00:13:20,090 --> 00:13:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the humans who possess 
unbreakable cores...</font>

166
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are capable of unleashing superhuman
 potential in whatever their specialty is.</font>

167
00:13:41,350 --> 00:13:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bat.</font>

168
00:13:44,470 --> 00:13:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't underestimate humans
if I were you.</font>

169
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:51,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're serious about 
doing something major...</font>

170
00:13:51,570 --> 00:13:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you'd better not let your guard down.</font>

171
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw you...</font>

172
00:13:58,330 --> 00:14:03,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way any monster 
could lose to a puny human!</font>

173
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, are you a friend of Kumota-san's?</font>

174
00:14:15,290 --> 00:14:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to join us for ramen?</font>

175
00:14:17,380 --> 00:14:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanna die, piggy?!</font>

176
00:14:25,070 --> 00:14:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can hardly stand living around
 these damn humans anymore.</font>

177
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanna talk about cores?</font>

178
00:14:36,410 --> 00:14:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then my core...</font>

179
00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is rage!</font>

180
00:15:52,410 --> 00:15:55,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we all set?</font>

181
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready!</font>

182
00:15:56,970 --> 00:15:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just you wait, Shocker!</font>

183
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will defeat you.</font>

184
00:16:10,620 --> 00:16:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

185
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

186
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:44,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to get underway.</font>

187
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:50,110
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}FUTABA'S PUB</b></font>

188
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to the schedule we found, 
 during the climax of the show...</font>

189
00:16:53,310 --> 00:16:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when excitement reaches its peak,
 the Bat Man will make his appearance.</font>

190
00:16:57,370 --> 00:17:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Combat Girls and other idols 
working as backup dancers</font>

191
00:17:00,690 --> 00:17:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will then convert the audience 
into Shocker combatants.</font>

192
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our goal is to stop that from happening.
But our real priority...</font>

193
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is ensuring the safety 
of everyone attending the show.</font>

194
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fifty-five thousand people
 will be in the audience.</font>

195
00:17:20,070 --> 00:17:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, we need to figure out
a way to evacuate them all.</font>

196
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can engage Shocker 
in battle, afterward.</font>

197
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For our point of entry,</font>

198
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukarisu and Nakao-san can pretend 
to be Shocker delivery people</font>

199
00:17:35,350 --> 00:17:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and smuggle us in.</font>

200
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once we're inside the service entrance, 
we'll take our individual positions.</font>

201
00:17:46,890 --> 00:17:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichiyo, you and Tojima-san will be 
on standby on the roof.</font>

202
00:17:51,110 --> 00:17:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's likely we'll need to start fighting
 as soon as the plan gets underway.</font>

203
00:17:56,840 --> 00:17:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you two to wait for the signal.</font>

204
00:18:00,910 --> 00:18:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're up against Shocker.</font>

205
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no telling what kind of 
unexpected trouble we'll run into.</font>

206
00:18:06,770 --> 00:18:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens, we'll have to use 
our individual judgment to deal with it.</font>

207
00:18:11,730 --> 00:18:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you two.</font>

208
00:18:14,490 --> 00:18:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop.</font>

209
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's inside those cases?</font>

210
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:22,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, seems to be 
additional pyrotechnics</font>

211
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for the second half of the concert.</font>

212
00:18:23,970 --> 00:18:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like, hey, maybe order 
the right amount to start!</font>

213
00:18:28,380 --> 00:18:29,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hear about this?</font>

214
00:18:29,980 --> 00:18:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure didn't.</font>

215
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's suspicious.</font>

216
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just to be safe, we're going to 
check the contents of—</font>

217
00:18:36,300 --> 00:18:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you guys let Master Bat Man know,</font>

218
00:18:39,390 --> 00:18:41,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">these last-second orders are real—</font>

219
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:43,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">—<i>Yeee</i>—</font>

220
00:18:43,530 --> 00:18:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">—tough to pull off.</font>

221
00:18:44,940 --> 00:18:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's so right! But since it's for 
our beloved Master Bat Man, w—</font>

222
00:18:49,980 --> 00:18:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">—<i>Yeee</i>—</font>

223
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">—don't mind putting in extra effort!</font>

224
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, then. Go on.</font>

225
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cop-<i>yeee </i>that!</font>

226
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a close one.</font>

227
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? If it isn't Aniki.</font>

228
00:19:32,170 --> 00:19:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while, Aniki.</font>

229
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, lately, you've 
been kinda down, Aniki.</font>

230
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, we were thinking about 
taking you to a show!</font>

231
00:19:50,860 --> 00:19:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's your favorite?</font>

232
00:19:53,090 --> 00:19:56,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd be pretty lucky 
to have three wives, Aniki!</font>

233
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A...</font>

234
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...ni...</font>

235
00:19:59,300 --> 00:20:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...ki...</font>

236
00:20:01,660 --> 00:20:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You guys...</font>

237
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're alive!</font>

238
00:20:08,690 --> 00:20:12,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on. I think they're...</font>

239
00:20:16,730 --> 00:20:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How? My boys...</font>

240
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... you're alive!</font>

241
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so... so relieved!</font>

242
00:20:37,460 --> 00:20:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm curious, though, Aniki.</font>

243
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

244
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:50,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the venue for a concert 
that Master Bat Man is hosting.</font>

245
00:20:51,490 --> 00:20:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master...?</font>

246
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't be trying to...</font>

247
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...disrupt Shocker's plan, would you?</font>

248
00:21:04,500 --> 00:21:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be... are you all...?</font>

249
00:21:20,170 --> 00:21:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

250
00:21:24,610 --> 00:21:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aniki. We're all...</font>

251
00:21:29,150 --> 00:21:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...members of Shocker now, too.</font>

252
00:21:43,670 --> 00:21:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And anyone who would defy us...</font>

253
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:50,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...must die.</font>

254
00:23:25,010 --> 00:23:28,010
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}NEXT EPISODE</b></font>

255
00:23:30,930 --> 00:23:33,140
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}LET'S DO THIS,</b></font>

256
00:23:33,140 --> 00:23:35,890
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}SHOCKER!</b></font>

257
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:40,020
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}LET'S DO THIS, SHOCKER!</b></font>

258
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:50,030
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}ILLUSTRATED BY: MIKIHIKO TABATA</b></font>

